Author:
Vol / Page:  103
Edition:
Quote:  By definition a boddler is a smallish person who is not really a baby but not quite a full-blown toddler. The expression, boddler boy, was copied after a mother from Waimahaka, in Southland, was savagely attacked by her 14-month-old son with a sawn-off rattle.
